{"tid":44010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一樣想屌柒港鐵嘅事","createTime":"2016-12-18T02:06:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T17:51:29.000Z","uid":45864,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"84fd51b6fc55d1081f662020e3a8b7f9cd74a7b3","tid":44010,"uid":45864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T02:06:40.000Z","msg":"港鐵正仆街 淨係識加價<br />\n朝早食唔切早餐 餓撚死都唔敢咬啖包 怕俾人罰錢<br />\n美孚行去西鐵站行到氣喘 水都唔敢飲啖<br />\nDllm真係好撚唔人道 <br />\n一人一句屌到港鐵肯俾人食野為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（清潔撚咪屌我）"},{"pid":"119793d12ec22f4b29122e8e72db38cf808aede4","tid":44010,"uid":5384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T02:13:27.000Z","msg":"畀大陸人拖巨型gip坐狗鐵<br />\n唔畀香港人帶樂器<br />\n正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03f3ec80acfa8a9c5366d0b17d50f52dad632ca","tid":44010,"uid":36480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T03:36:13.000Z","msg":"無話唔比你飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64586bf83f147b46b3418c2cb58847b5f43b20f4","tid":44010,"uid":49250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T03:48:48.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 成撚日整埋 小恩小惠 <br />\n有加無減又成日壞車 我屌你老母"},{"pid":"bd61e49b301baf081f7d013a6ef53b16313700e4","tid":44010,"uid":64605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T03:51:09.000Z","msg":"毎次係調景嶺轉車都想屌柒港鐡，你懂的"},{"pid":"a263183c0803141069f8135db7fd22c541f16ce0","tid":44010,"uid":17427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"